I know, Clow Lord. I was just saying.

::FZ/DevilDuer::

FZ falls with a hole in his chest. He tries to jump up but his legs don't 
respond. He growls. "Why a-" FZ never gets to finis his sentence as DevilDuer 
kicks him in the head, knocking him unconscious.

"Where do you want him?" DevilDuer asks, looking at his superior.
